Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總統閣下 交易順利完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必您明天就能看到Little Comet的光芒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什麼呢 快點開車
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.07,0:01:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了 能出示一下您的身份證嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.92,0:01:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個旗子你沒有看見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.00,0:01:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是瑪蘭達共和國的特命全權大使
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是國際問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.82,0:01:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀 真對不起 我不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.94,0:01:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大使
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼 那可是外交公用車啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.28,0:02:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快閃開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,180,,{\fnFZDaBiaoSong-B06\bord0\fs65\fad(500,300)\blur0\t(3610,3710,\blur10)}東杜拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.18,0:02:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來就是一條路直通寶藏了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「東杜拉世界著名歌手奎因·瑪露塔在西杜拉被暗殺」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「東西杜拉之間的互不侵犯條約被撕毀 邦交關係緊張」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然破壞意在和平的互不侵犯條約
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西杜拉可是會變成世界公敵的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真搞不懂他們在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本明明是一個國家 卻把無辜的人牽連進來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 你還在介意那件事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本來應該能保護她的 僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.06,0:03:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不想死成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這城市還真不太平
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡的犯罪防範率之高可謂世界首屈一指
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟東杜拉可是聚集了享譽全球的優等生們的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才會有各種大使館和資本家豪宅林立嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直是盜賊聖地對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是希望他們能夠手下留情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有行李
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠道而來辛苦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不說這個了 那個東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請往這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是傳說在中世紀墜落在東杜拉的彗星的碎片 Little Comet
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1604,980)}小彗星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:40.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東杜拉也太沒眼光了 居然放棄這樣的珍寶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就證明他們有更渴望獲得的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指的是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是西杜拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們用這顆寶石換取了我國的鈾濃縮設備
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的用途並不難想像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一群蠢蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:05:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我們瑪蘭達共和國只是站在中立的立場上出售軍火
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至於其用途則不是我們該干涉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請您親手把玩欣賞一番吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是輸入解鎖密碼的打字機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴露了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.76,0:05:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次元 你做什麼啊 我還沒問到密碼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒時間給你喋喋不休了 準備開溜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動作未免太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不記得露出過馬腳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來只能從這走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.54,0:06:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 他們幹得還真漂亮嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.94,0:06:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.76,0:06:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直就像把我們的行動都看穿了似的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.76,0:06:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯邦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是普通市民的汽車啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種野蠻行徑我可幹不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒交通工具就只能乾瞪眼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該死 上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.14,0:07:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.12,0:07:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次元
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯邦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可原諒 那個開槍狙擊我們的傢伙是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種子彈 我見過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 在哪裡見到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奎因·瑪露塔那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,150,,{\fnFZDaBiaoSong-B06\fs90\bord0\fad(300,500)}7天前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,70,,{\fnFZDaBiaoSong-B06\fs55\bord0\fad(300,100)\blur0\t(2940,3340,\blur10)\b0}西杜拉 國際音樂會會場
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衝我們開槍的就是那個槍殺了奎因·瑪露塔的傢伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.06,0:09:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能完全確定就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們怎麼找到這兒的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是優等生之城啊 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有點事需要確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:09:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在找什麼 次元
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.44,0:10:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你難道是幽靈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾經聽說過一個傳言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個叫耶爾·奧崎的殺手會為他目標提前立一塊墓碑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.96,0:10:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他從不主動殺人 只接受他人的委託
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還從來沒聽說過 他是個什麼角色？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的情報幾乎是一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟從來沒人在被他盯上之後還能活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道 他好像對自己的槍法非常自信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會丟骰子決定用幾發子彈了結目標
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕廟會似的興奮 愉快的心情 勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你突然嘀咕什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.49,0:10:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是香芹的花語
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有就是死亡的前兆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說他很享受殺人的工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你贏得了他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這話我可不能當作沒聽到啊 難道你覺得我會輸？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是沒人活下來麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你還帶傷 太不利了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界第一的槍手不需要兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是為朋友著想才勸你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要搞錯了 我們只是生意上的搭檔而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是什麼朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 這樣啊 那就隨便你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能請到您這樣的美女 我們深感榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 你真是嘴甜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本俱樂部採用會員制度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:12:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來客都是溫文爾雅的資本家 不必擔心會有麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼在表演時間到來前就請您在此等候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:13:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表演馬上就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 都這個點了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讓人為難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.42,0:13:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不是您這樣的女士該得到的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快把我放下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想殺我嗎 次元大介
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.44,0:13:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯邦三世 你怎麼找到這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:35.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒注意到嗎 供奉在你墓前的是原生香芹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還帶有微弱的銀蓮花的香氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.06,0:13:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這附近沒多少開著大片銀蓮花的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒打算要別人幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別多心 我可不是來幫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是很好奇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰出於什麼目的僱用了耶爾·奧崎想要幹掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:14:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顯然是想要奪回大使館寶物的那群傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那為什麼沒準備我的墓碑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得這事有蹊蹺 所以我來確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好事了小心送命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這句話我原封不動地還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經荒廢了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來這裡不像是他的基地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個槍械工房嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.68,0:14:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快進去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.14,0:14:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別推我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.08,0:14:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊全是通訊設備
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 過來看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,興趣還挺廣泛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.18,0:14:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來他的手挺巧的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼搞的 全都是一樣的西服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普拉達嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(932,980)}Prada
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次元你也穿的同一個牌子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我穿的牌子可多了 從紀梵希到芬迪都有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1306,980)}FENDI
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1090,980)}GIVENCHY
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.88,0:15:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}快放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不二子的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.76,0:15:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.16,0:15:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不二子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.06,0:15:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不二子 能聽見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這聲音…是魯邦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被耶爾·奧崎給盯上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本來想到俱樂部當舞孃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果好像不小心誤闖了個不得了的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.52,0:15:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在盤算什麼 不二子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說得那麼難聽嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只不過是想金盆洗手而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是可能是報應不爽了吧 看樣子我玩完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 你可別說這種不吉利的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是說真的 魯邦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你可別來救我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.52,0:16:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我不想連累你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永別了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還真是被看扁了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 你以為我是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行不行不試一下怎麼知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼你要試試看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事要問你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.28,0:16:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你要監視不二子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.26,0:16:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女人我並不認識
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在確認我佈置的東西的運作情況而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你為什麼要殺次元
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有什麼理由 我只管解決目標
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你有點得意忘形了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個狙擊手這麼靠近他的目標怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有人開槍能比次元更快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你犯了兩個錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 我擅長的不僅僅是狙擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其次 在開槍速度上是你們不及我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就讓我來試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:16:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還欠了你一筆賬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.82,0:17:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我就跟你算清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要用左手來比試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 隨便你什麼時候拔槍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次元輸了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,.357馬格努 這種大口徑子彈不適合速射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 餘興節目到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次元大介 下一發子彈就會要了你的命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形勢對你不利 暫時先撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我 魯邦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少廢話 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的沒想到你會在速射上輸掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的槍是點22口徑 很小
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且改造得非常輕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你也用那種槍就不會輸了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是意氣用事的時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不給他一發子彈我嚥不下這口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給你了 次元
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.76,0:19:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次元 抓緊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什麼啊喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.22,0:19:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是用骰子來決定開幾槍的嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可能有什麼個人堅持的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼才管他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活該
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.54,0:20:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭 這是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算甩掉他了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.66,0:21:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下他應該追不上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會找他一雪前恥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.02,0:21:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 他一定有盲點的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯邦 他又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是難纏的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.26,0:21:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次元…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒路了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.52,0:22:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.46,0:22:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.62,0:22:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他瞄準我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.26,0:22:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不穿過對面的倉庫就逃不掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.94,0:22:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就只能上了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.04,0:22:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢著 一衝出去就成他槍下亡魂了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.72,0:22:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別把話說得這麼簡單 我可不能死在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.22,0:22:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我 次元
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心 他是沒法連我們什麼時候衝出去都預測到的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.60,0:22:50.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我數到三 我們一起朝對面倉庫衝過去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.72,0:22:52.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 這不就是在搏命嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.06,0:22:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的目標可是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.50,0:22:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞砸了我就變成鬼一輩子纏著你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.92,0:22:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我可不願意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.40,0:22:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.20,0:23:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.20,0:23:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.96,0:23:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.82,0:23:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二 三！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.06,0:23:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次元 喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.90,0:23:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次元 堅持住
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.07,0:23:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 次元
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.20,0:23:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,親眼看著朋友被殺的感覺如何
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.22,0:23:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照你那魯莽的計劃行事 就會落到這個下場
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.66,0:23:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在你知道自己有多無能了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.50,0:23:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你槍法好這點我很清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.78,0:23:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是要我來說 你本人就是一把槍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.82,0:23:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果沒有人委託你 幫你扣動扳機
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.10,0:23:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就只是個打不出子彈的工具而已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.56,0:23:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你該慶幸這一點 你是因此才撿回一條命的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.68,0:24:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…
